{
  "stem": "4764.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother had a sister in America.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said-- they took quite a few people and said, you will now be deported to-- deported, I suppose we would all like to be deported from there-- to America.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were taken from this ghetto in Bochnia to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were standing, and the part that I remember was there were these huge logs standing outside-- out at the back of this huge building, which I suppose must have been some sort of official building.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were standing there for hours in the cold waiting to be admitted to this-- to this place, which was going to be a-- a focus of-- of being taken out from there, by train I assume.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after many hours of standing out in the cold with my parents on these huge logs-- which obviously weren't as big, but to me, they seemed huge-- we were taken into this huge hole-- again, it probably wasn't as huge, but again, then, because I'm small-- I was small.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we wait-- we stayed there for quite a few days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were taken back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was-- I'm not quite sure why they did this, but it is something that I remember well because my parents had thought, this is going to be it, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are going to be rescued.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember when that happened?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I think it happened about-- maybe about two years after we were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite a while after we actually went there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- it was-- I can't understand what the reason was.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
